title: Nintendo 3DS Carrying Case Compatible With Nintendo Switch, 2DS, 3DS, 3DS XL, DS, DS XL, DS Light Handle & Shoulder Strap Traveling Carry Case With Hard Zipper Blue Officially licensed
features: UNIVERSAL CAPABILITY: Our Nintendo Officially licensed carrying case is specially designed & is compatible with the majority of Nintendo systems: Nintendo 3DS XL, Nintendo 3DS, New 3DS XL, New 3DS, New 2DS XL and of course Nintendo Switch.

MAJOR CAPACITY: With 1 external and 2 internal pockets lined with microfiber material you are sure to have optimal space and protection! Wall Chargers, accessories, cameras, tablets, headphones even your snacks are welcome with enough space for all! Also included is 4 game flexible organizing folder!

PROTECTION FIRST: Crowned with sleek polyester exterior, after opening our Velcro first layer protection the heart of the case is secured with a strong metal zipper. CARRY IN STYLE: Lightweight and comfortable handle, or strap around your shoulder with the included shoulder strap accessories. With a variety of colors available you are sure to travel and carry in comfort and style.

OFFICIALLY LICENSED: Dress your Nintendo system with Official Nintendo Clothing! Highest quality material and designed specifically for Nintendo products. Not satisfied? No problem, no question asked warranty comes with our product!
description: You'll have tons of room to store any Nintendo DS System and up to 4 DS or 3DS Game Cards with the Universal Super Mario Transporter Case. Keep it all safe with a secure flap, and store extra DS accessories in the zipper pocket. Made to take any Nintendo DS System on the go, you can carry it all in this great case using the handle or the shoulder strap.
